name: The Celestial Tribe
description: Celestial tribes known as pacifists grew up in harmony with nature and taught science in creating an early civilization. Some of their discoveries such as herbal concoctions, the science of farming, and building the largest library of their time. A library that can satisfy the curiosity of the mysteries in the world. The sequence of events that have been recorded in the Kot collection (an elongated sheet of paper generated from the Kot Tree).
